{"tid":1886784,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[九唔搭八]被問上市公司匯報卻答口罩供應　劉怡翔被指「發夢」","createTime":"2020-02-19T06:42:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-19T07:10:01.000Z","uid":51271,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d1e2e3c30e00fe11d5fe1d26c35b9097b4137b51","tid":1886784,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T06:42:06.000Z","msg":"立法會就政府應對新型肺炎措施進行急切口頭質詢，有議員就上市公司匯報提問，官員回應時則談口罩供應，被議員批評「發夢」。<br />\n<br />\n金融服務界張華峰關注，受疫情影響，在內地有業務的上市公司能否延遲公布年報，以免因為沒有依時公布而觸犯上市條例，甚至被停牌。<br />\n<br />\n財經事務及庫務局局長劉怡翔回應時，卻談及物流署口罩供應情況。主席梁君彥隨即提出，議員是關注上市公司匯報問題。劉怡翔再請張華峰重複問題，引起多名在席議員不滿，張華峰說，已提出有關問題。<br />\n<br />\n民主黨林卓廷批評劉怡翔月薪數十萬，卻在立法會會議上「發夢」。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1509435-20200219.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1509435-20200219.htm&d=WZLdF6k3LRQ%2Bb7h5E4OoDsyZng7V5AOcQmv89xdKlzQ%3D&h=882dae1d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1509435-20200219.htm&h=1ff0a81c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1509435-20200219.htm</a>"},{"pid":"aab44a8a5aa5bf2c5198ce20382a8c8032a8ccb1","tid":1886784,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T06:54:59.000Z","msg":"狗官"},{"pid":"69441aae3eec3cb9b8e2fb5208d55e40452c09b9","tid":1886784,"uid":217189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T06:56:02.000Z","msg":"垃圾 浪費公帑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18c11329ae9cb3fefaf998f1eeed29bf527fcc30","tid":1886784,"uid":60831,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T06:57:01.000Z","msg":"竟然俾張華鋒隻肥豬陰到<br />\n屌你老母笑撚死，衰係自己人手上 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/as